data.description: OPEN HOUSE 7/22 1-3 PM In the heart of Dignowity, this wonderfully updated home with its open floorplan, high ceilings and abundant natural light has plenty of character and charm. Fresh paint throughout the home. Welcoming front porch and back deck with access from the master suite give plenty of space to relax and entertain. Gourmet kitchen with gas cooking, granite counters, and accent lighting. The unique barn doors and kitchen island are made from reclaimed wood original to the 1917 home. A large yard gives lots of opportunities to garden, storage shed. Come feel the love in this home!
